<p rend="chapter">(13) 3. Parisuddhavaggavaṇṇanā</p>

<p rend="bodytext" n="123"><hi rend="paranum">123</hi><hi rend="dot">.</hi> Tatiyassa <pb ed="P" n="5.0074" /> paṭhame <hi rend="bold">parisuddhā</hi>ti nimmalā. <hi rend="bold">Pariyodātā</hi>ti pabhassarā. Dutiyādīni uttānatthānevāti.</p>

<p rend="centre">Parisuddhavaggo tatiyo.</p>
